data.description:
Odaily Planet Daily News Bubblemaps published a post on the X platform saying that it will split the token supply on Solana and BNB chains, of which the BMT deployer address holds 757 million tokens on Solana, accounting for 75% of the total supply, of which about 348.8 million have been deposited in the vested contract operator on Solana, and about 408.1 million tokens have been bridged to BNB Chain using LayerZero OFT. According to token economics, the supply on BNB Chain has been allocated and fully locked on Unicrypt, including: 
1. Protocol development/R&D: 60 million; 
2. Team (now and in the future): 90 million; 
3. Ecosystem: 206.7 million; 
4. Liquidity: 51.45 million.
